snippet.title: Trailer Supernatural: The Game
snippet.description:
Supernatural: The Game from the Russian game studio Red Star Games. The project is being created with enthusiasm, at the expense of personal funds from the developers and the support of fans of the series. The game will be released before the end of the year and will be available on VK Play for FREE. There will also be 2 Russian voiceovers to choose from in the game, in 1 version of Dean Winchester was voiced by Mikhail Tikhonov (voiced by RenTV), in 2 versions of the character was voiced by Mikhail Khrustalev (voiced by LostFilm). There will also be English subtitles in the game.

The events of the game will tell the story of Dean Winchester's formation as an independent hunter of evil spirits and will be a prequel to the original series.

#redstargames #supernaturalthegame #final
